ATTRIBUTION OF ANALYTICAL METHODS
================================================================

The scientific methods implemented by the Suite are documented in
docs/methods.md. Key references:

  Dunn et al. (Capacitive vs diffusion decomposition)
      Wang, J.; Polleux, J.; Lim, J.; Dunn, B.
      J. Phys. Chem. C 2007, 111, 14925.

  ECASA / Cdl methodology
      McCrory, C. C. L.; Jung, S.; Peters, J. C.; Jaramillo, T. F.
      J. Am. Chem. Soc. 2013, 135, 16977.

  Randles–Sevcik equation
      Bard, A. J.; Faulkner, L. R.
      Electrochemical Methods: Fundamentals and Applications, 2nd ed.
      Wiley, 2001.

These references describe the methods implemented; they do not
imply endorsement of this Software by the original authors.

